ActIndian Act
SubjectOrder Accepting the Surrender of a Portion of Cowichan Lake Indian Reserve - Ts'uubaa-asatx Surrender Agreement
PrecisOrder accepting the absolute SURRENDER made to His Majesty in right of Canada by Ts'uubaa-asatx of a portion of COWICHAN LAKE INDIAN RESERVE, in British Columbia, which was assented to by Ts'uubaa-asatx on March 31, 2022, in order to use the reserve lands for public highway purposes.
